---
title: Roast Pumpkin, Beef & Capsicum Relish Orecchiette with Courgette & Feta
description: Orecchiette is the carb that keeps on giving. This dish is packed with cherry tomatoes, beef mince and our chargrilled capsicum relish lending richness and flavour to perfectly cooked orecchiette. Let’s top it with roasted veggies and crumbly, creamy feta for a meal that wil warm your soul all year round.

*We’ve replaced the risoni in this recipe with orecchiette due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
